\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
How do transfers interact with labor market formality? Should transfers
 be made conditional on having (previously held) formal work?
\begin_inset VSpace smallskip
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
How can governments reduce the administrative burden of enforcing conditionality
/eligibility? What role does technology play in this?
\begin_inset VSpace smallskip
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
What types of transfer programs face the fewest political economy challenges?
 In what circumstances will governments adopt what types of policies?
\begin_inset VSpace smallskip
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Who should administer transfer programs? What level of government? How much
 to rely on self-reporting? 
\begin_inset VSpace smallskip
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
How much do eligibility requirements reduce incentives to graduate out of
 eligibility? To stay in rural areas?
\end_layout

\end_deeper
